{"tid":1096082,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑自己抑鬱/情緒病","createTime":"2019-04-07T13:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T20:25:55.000Z","uid":71204,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b1481ee0bd1d2cc646cdb74f659f07b3180d055c","tid":1096082,"uid":71204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:01:38.000Z","msg":"情緒時好時壞<br />\n壞起上嚟成個weekend 匿埋係屋企喊<br />\n控制唔到自己諗野好負面 <br />\n做咩都唔成功 覺得自己好廢好想死<br />\n有諗過其實燒碳自殺唔難 <br />\n好彩仲返到工 未累及屋企人<br />\n近1年都唔想參與任何社交活動 <br />\n比面會出席下但成日放朋友飛機<br />\n<br />\n有醫生/TG grouo推介嗎？"},{"pid":"4f503c556d58e0894f9dad2ff7ca4dadb4b32fe5","tid":1096082,"uid":72690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:04:13.000Z","msg":"仲有冇其他唔舒服"},{"pid":"9cbb3775a7e2732974c4b2f1991d8ba674af75c2","tid":1096082,"uid":241021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:07:56.000Z","msg":"唔好諗自殺啦。雖然自殺令你唔洗經歷往後既困難同壓力，但同時係放棄往後人生既快樂。"},{"pid":"8aaf474e732a9d4841842c36357b3f8857d353c6","tid":1096082,"uid":71204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:07:59.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n由兩年前成日肩頸痛開始<br />\n連情緒都成日唔好<br />\n啲腳同膝頭都痛<br />\n<br />\n利申：2字尾"},{"pid":"3b3e35d9192539e1bfe537c5d704b9ee77f9d2b7","tid":1096082,"uid":71204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cbb3775a7e2732974c4b2f1991d8ba674af75c2","tid":1096082,"uid":241021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:07:56.000Z","msg":"唔好諗自殺啦。雖然自殺令你唔洗經歷往後既困難同壓力，但同時係放棄往後人生既快樂。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"但傷心好像大過快樂<br />\n失敗左好多次<br />\n對自己冇信心"},{"pid":"9f375de4ebbdf21693888ad00a9a744c9dcc28b9","tid":1096082,"uid":193020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:26:50.000Z","msg":"其實咁大個人 相信好多野你都明 問題只係做唔做到<br />\n跳晒啲無謂問題吧<br />\n<br />\n問一條比較重要既問題<br />\n如果你想有人幫到你 你會希望果個人做啲咩？<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/KK4997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FKK4997&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=e330e56c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/KK4997</a>"},{"pid":"b39b74cfb9c3ea2b110fcc95bd177d6285b144ef","tid":1096082,"uid":59492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aaf474e732a9d4841842c36357b3f8857d353c6","tid":1096082,"uid":71204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:07:59.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n由兩年前成日肩頸痛開始<br />\n連情緒都成日唔好<br />\n啲腳同膝頭都痛<br />\n<br />\n利申：2字尾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:31:02.000Z","msg":"我29"},{"pid":"625774f9229381a60147f74423bbd13376d7b091","tid":1096082,"uid":186297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97704059adb467faa485ef3a9affaaa4c914c0d6","tid":1096082,"uid":96823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自從同女朋友散左之後<br />\n一直都接受唔到<br />\n好似開心唔返咁"},{"pid":"7bd48de7a61aaab0fbfa4a2ee824c1d2f21be70e","tid":1096082,"uid":122513,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b1481ee0bd1d2cc646cdb74f659f07b3180d055c","tid":1096082,"uid":71204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:01:38.000Z","msg":"情緒時好時壞<br />\n壞起上嚟成個weekend 匿埋係屋企喊<br />\n控制唔到自己諗野好負面 <br />\n做咩都唔成功 覺得自己好廢好想死<br />\n有諗過其實燒碳自殺唔難 <br />\n好彩仲返到工 未累及屋企人<br />\n近1年都唔想參與任何社交活動 <br />\n比面會出席下但成日放朋友飛機<br />\n<br />\n有醫生/TG grouo推介嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T07:12:25.000Z","msg":"看來你心中的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀．．．人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=416dc027\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=cbdd2ecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。</a> 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"2933d7b3b6128da6c7cb54362b208a703644f467","tid":1096082,"uid":22736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"97704059adb467faa485ef3a9affaaa4c914c0d6","tid":1096082,"uid":96823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自從同女朋友散左之後<br />\n一直都接受唔到<br />\n好似開心唔返咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:18:37.000Z","msg":"香港男小女多怕鳩冇女人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93beae2b3b765a64cd9c79c0af38998dc85069fe","tid":1096082,"uid":132942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"Same... 無力感孤單感很強烈...<br />\n雖然有穩定收入 但不敢諗未來 不敢諗有自己嘅居所<br />\n覺得冇咩事情值得自己去追求<br />\n人越大反而越唔會想向朋友傾吐心聲<br />\n一來可能越來越怕暴露自己軟弱嘅一面<br />\n二來根本幫唔到啲乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22f400975ca8d9c236a66f710d573d73b4a46b8","tid":1096082,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:27:01.000Z","msg":"如果負擔得起請儘快向私家精神科醫生求助因為有啲嚴重"},{"pid":"1bfe7e8f6b8a83221653675a83289c6e68820b78","tid":1096082,"uid":45355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93beae2b3b765a64cd9c79c0af38998dc85069fe","tid":1096082,"uid":132942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"Same... 無力感孤單感很強烈...<br />\n雖然有穩定收入 但不敢諗未來 不敢諗有自己嘅居所<br />\n覺得冇咩事情值得自己去追求<br />\n人越大反而越唔會想向朋友傾吐心聲<br />\n一來可能越來越怕暴露自己軟弱嘅一面<br />\n二來根本幫唔到啲乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T09:38:18.000Z","msg":"Same here <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7852e1b2144df857eecdebafb37a108d879dab5","tid":1096082,"uid":113546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T20:25:55.000Z","msg":"反而好驚聽到啲勵志嘢<br />\n咩心態決定境界喱類.......<br />\n就係太清楚知道自己能力<br />\n但又未徹底接受一世打牛工嘅命運<br />\n可以話係冇自信<br />\n又可以話係自我設限<br />\n姐係要等自己去突破困局<br />\n但我戰勝唔到心魔<br />\n我都好抑鬱"}]}